  "description": "This is a living page that I will consistently update as I continue to progress as a programmer.\r Currently this page only uses HTML, CSS, and Javascript (jQuery), but I have tried to set it up to emulate a full stack web application with a front-end and back-end section.\r ### About Me\r The \"About Me\" section outlines where I currently am as a programmer and maybe some potential future endeavours I may pursue.\r ### Projects\r The \"Projects\" section displays projects that I have worked on either in school or on my personal time.\r This will contain a overall accumulation of all of the projects I have completed with links to the source code.\r ### Contact \r The \"Contact\" section will contact information and github link.\r Both the phone number and email will be copied to the clipboard on-click.",
